  <h1> Multiple Values Padding</h1>
<p>An element's padding is the space between its content and its border. With multiple values, one can shift the padding of each of the four respective sides.</p>
  
<h2>2 values change opposite side as a pair. The first one will change the top and bottom while the second value will change the left and right <br> Padding: 35px 400px</h2>
